  <h1>To use the Public GeyserConnect for your Xbox,</h1>
  <p>go to <code>Settings>General>Network>Advanced Settings>DNS Settings</code> to change the Primary DNS setting of
    your Xbox to</p>

  <h3><span class="primary-dns"></span></h3>
  <img src="/images/screenshots/xbox-dns.png" class="img-fluid" alt="Xbox DNS Screenshot" id="screenshot">

  <p>and your Secondary DNS as</p>
  <h3>your "Gateway IP", "8.8.8.8", or "1.1.1.1"</h3>
  <img src="/images/screenshots/xbox-dns2.png" class="img-fluid" alt="Xbox DNS Screenshot 2" id="screenshot">
  <p>P.S. This will not work if you have IPv6 enabled on your network. You will either need to disable IPv6 in your
    router, or use our <a ref="/guide/friendslist">Friends List method.</a></p>
